            <note xml:id="foot.f2">Geikie refers to <ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_2772.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">Geikie 1868</ref>; see <ref target="./DCP-LETT-8112.xml" resp="#mjhawkins" cert="high">letter to Archibald Geikie, 20 December 1871</ref> and n. 3.</note>
